# Where the dashboard reads analyzer artifacts from.
# Resolution priority: these env vars > ../config.json work dir (local dev) >
# the committed web/snapshot/ (deploy). Copy to .env.local to use.

# A repo-layout root containing work/ (handy for pointing at a fixture/checkout):
# HJ_DATA_ROOT=/absolute/path/to/hackathon-judges

# Or point directly at a work dir:
# HJ_WORK_DIR=/absolute/path/to/work
